quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  39,75,"O sì máa rí àwọn Mọlāika tí wọ́n ń rọkiriká ní àyíká Ìtẹ́-ọlá. Wọ́n ń ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ àti ìdúpẹ́ fún Olúwa wọn. A máa fi òdodo ṣèdájọ́ láààrin àwọn ẹ̀dá. Wọ́n sì máa sọ pé: “Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá.”",""
  40,1,"Hā mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1."
  40,2,"Tírà náà sọ̀kalẹ̀ díẹ̀ díẹ̀ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu, Alágbára, Onímọ̀,",""
  40,3,"Aláforíjìn-ẹ̀ṣẹ̀, Olùgba-ìronúpìwàdà, Ẹni líle níbi ìyà, Ọlọ́rẹ, kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ máa jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. Ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ ni àbọ̀ ẹ̀dá.",""
  40,4,"Kò sí ẹni tí ó máa ṣe àtakò sí àwọn āyah Allāhu àfi àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́. Nítorí náà, má ṣe jẹ́ kí ìgbòkègbodò wọn nínú ìlú kó ẹ̀tàn bá ọ.",""
  40,5,"Ìjọ (Ànábì) Nūh pe òdodo ní irọ́ ṣíwájú wọn. Àwọn ìjọ (mìíràn) lẹ́yìn wọn (náà ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀). Ìjọ kọ̀ọ̀kan ló gbèrò láti ki Òjíṣẹ́ wọn mọ́lẹ̀. Wọ́n fi irọ́ ja òdodo níyàn nítorí kí wọ́n lè fi wó òdodo lulẹ̀. Mo sì gbá wọn mú. Nítorí náà, báwo ni ìyà (tí Mo fi jẹ wọ́n) ti rí (lára wọn ná)!",""
  40,6,"Àti pé báyẹn ni ọ̀rọ̀ Olúwa rẹ ṣe kò lórí àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ pé: “Dájúdájú àwọn ni èrò inú Iná.”",""
  40,7,"Àwọn tó gbé Ìtẹ́-ọlá náà rù àti àwọn tó wà ní àyíká rẹ̀, wọ́n ń ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú ìdúpẹ́ fún Olúwa wọn. Wọ́n ní ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo nínú Allāhu. Wọ́n sì ń tọrọ àforíjìn fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo (báyìí pé): “Olúwa wa, ìkẹ́ àti ìmọ̀ (Rẹ) gbòòrò ju gbogbo n̄ǹkan lọ, nítorí náà, ṣàforíjìn fún àwọn tó ronú pìwàdà, tí wọ́n sì tẹ̀lé ojú-ọ̀nà Rẹ. Kí O sì ṣọ́ wọn nínú ìyà iná Jẹhīm.",""
